lesson-1
fork serpentcloud to your repo.
Check it out, then create a new branch lesson1
create a folder lesson1
in that folder create a file named README.md
in that README.md file add these tasks: 
Task-1:
  create new ssh key
  put key on github
  test key on dev machine
Task-2:
  start task server
  log in to task server: http://serpent.cloud 
  create a user
  wait for "first task" to be assinged
  then review how to manage the ticket and begin working on lesson1-task3 ticket
